关闭fcitx预编辑?
csslayer:退出之后,改~/.config/fcitx/profile PreeditStringInClientWindow=False
vim /usr/share/fcitx/configdesc/profile.desc
关闭fcitx组合键C-;功能,因为与emacs绑定键冲突
/usr/share/fcitx/addon/fcitx-clipboard.conf添加Enabled=False
或者~/.config/fcitx/conf/fcitx-clipboard.config

fcitx in debian jessie report error "Connection Error (/usr/bin/dbus-lauch 
terminated abnormally without any error message), the reason is debian don't
install dbus-x11, aptitude install dbus-x11 then restart fcitx with fcitx -rd will
be fine.
